data.description: Wonderful home in City View that offers ample space for comfortable living. The living room with a 9-foot ceiling & beautiful fireplace creates a cozy and inviting atmosphere. The kitchen/dining combo provides a functional and stylish space. It's a great area for cooking and entertaining. The isolated primary suite, features a 9-foot ceiling, offers a private retreat. The ensuite bathroom with a jetted tub, separate shower, and a walk-in closet adds a luxurious touch. The backyard with an 8-foot privacy fence is a fantastic outdoor space for relaxation and entertaining. It provides a sense of privacy and security, making it an ideal place for family gatherings or enjoying the outdoors. This home appears to have many desirable features, making it a comfortable and stylish place to live.
